title: Young Thug Teases Possible Collaboration with The Weeknd
text:
Just hours prior, Young Thug took to his personal Instagram account to hint that he may be teaming up with Canadian superstar The Weeknd. Posting a picture of the duo, the No, My Name is JEFFERY rapper added the caption "OTW!!!" Unfortunately, no other details were given at this time as for when the record will arrive or what it'll be off of, but it'll probably be pretty fire. Are you excited at the possible team up? Stay tuned for more details. 
OTW!!! 
A photo posted by ""JEFFERY"" (@thuggerthugger1) on Jan 6, 2017 at 7:04pm PST
